Description: hyd1d provides an S4 class, datasets and several functions to
    interpolate 1D water levels with gauging data. The S4 class
    WaterLevelDataFrame structures the computation and visualisation of 1D
    water level information along the German federal waterways Elbe and Rhine.
    hyd1d delivers 1D water level data - provided by the FLYS database - and 
    validated gauging data - provided by the hydrological database HyDaBa -
    package-internally. For computations near realtime data are queried
    externally from PEGELONLINE.
